'''Organización de Telecomunicaciones de Iberoamérica''' (OTI), formerly known as '''Organizacão de Televisão Ibero-Americana''' (OTI) or "Organization of Iberoamerican Television" (OIT), is an organization of [[television]] [[television network|networks]] in [[Latin America]] ([[Ibero-America]]), [[Spain]], and [[Portugal]]. Its mission is to foster relations between television networks in [[Spanish language|Spanish]] and [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]] speaking countries. Among other activities, it shares news, cultural, educational and sports programming among its members.

